# 💬 Chat & Messaging API Documentation

## 📍 Base URL

```bash id="9r2m1x"
http://localhost:5000/chat
```

---

# 🧭 Overview

This module allows authenticated users to:

* Send and receive messages داخل الفريق
* Upload and share files
* Track message seen status
* Receive notifications

🔐 **All routes require authentication (JWT)**

---

# 🔐 Authentication

Every request must include:

```http id="6w3qkp"
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
```

---

# 💬 1. Get Team Messages

## 🔗 Endpoint

```bash id="7y8v4n"
GET /chat/team/:teamId/messages
```

## 🔐 Auth Required

✅ Yes

## 📌 URL Params

```bash id="p0k5zd"
teamId = ID of the team
```

## ✅ Response

```json id="x2n4bm"
[
  {
    "id": 1,
    "team_id": 1,
    "sender_id": 5,
    "message": "Hello team!",
    "mssg_type": "text",
    "file_url": null,
    "created_at": "2026-04-17T10:00:00Z"
  }
]
```

