# 📎 5. Send File Message

## 🔗 Endpoint

```bash id="z1x9vb"
POST /chat/send-file
```

## 🔐 Auth Required

✅ Yes

## 📥 Request Type

`multipart/form-data`

## 📥 Form Data

| Key    | Type | Description    |
| ------ | ---- | -------------- |
| file   | File | File to upload |
| teamId | Int  | Team ID        |

---

## ✅ Response

```json id="n4m8yc"
{
  "message": "File sent",
  "file": "/uploads/1713360000-uuid.pdf"
}
```

---

## ❌ Error Responses

```json id="h2p6ks"
{ "message": "No file uploaded" }
{ "message": "Not a team member" }
```

