# 💻 Frontend Examples

## 🧪 Get Messages

```js id="l6r2wd"
await fetch(`/chat/team/${teamId}/messages`, {
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  }
});
```

---

## 🧪 Send Text Message

```js id="y9q4te"
await fetch("/chat/send", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({
    teamId: 1,
    message: "Hello!"
  })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Send File

```js id="g5n8vx"
const formData = new FormData();
formData.append("file", selectedFile);
formData.append("teamId", 1);

await fetch("/chat/send-file", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: formData
});
```

---

## 🧪 Mark as Seen

```js id="u1k7oz"
await fetch("/chat/seen", {
  method: "POST",
  headers: {
    "Content-Type": "application/json",
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ teamId: 1 })
});
```

---

## 🧪 Get Notifications

```js id="b4m9qs"
await fetch("/chat/notifications", {
  headers: {
    Authorization: `Bearer ${token}`
  }
});
```

