# ⚠️ Important Notes

## 🔴 Authentication

* All routes are protected
* Missing/invalid token → `401 Unauthorized`

---

## 🔴 Authorization

* User must be a member of the team to:

  * send messages
  * upload files
  * view messages

---

## 🔴 File Upload Rules (Recommended)

* Max file size (e.g. 5MB)
* Allowed types: PDF, DOCX, PNG, JPG

---

## 🔴 Security

* Validate file uploads to prevent malicious files
* Store files securely (consider cloud storage later)

---

